{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Overview:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are an Alchemist with a fatal illness. You traveled to a hidden valley where you hope to find a cure. A dark story with alchemy, exploration and light-deck building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/ImageA.png?t=1738147454\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Improve your Actions through Deck Building:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use cards from <strong>THREE</strong> different decks to explore, gather herbs, rest and create potions. Build your decks by adding Passive, Action or Alchemy cards, or replace existing cards to help you in your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/ImageC2.png?t=1738147454\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build the World through Exploration:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world grows through your actions. Place lakes, fields, and forests while exploring, each containing herbs to help you in crafting potions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/ImageB.png?t=1738147454\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Craft cures and potions through Alchemy:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While your herbs are the ingredients, your Alchemy cards are powerful tools to modify them. Create a variety of potions to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/ImageD2.png?t=1738147454\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But things are rarely as simple as they seem. Dangers are roam